  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    airQualityAnalytics
    this class is going to be redirecting the user into the real-time air quality page where we are going to be visualizing the real time change of data in a bar graph there is also going to be the use of a ListView in order to see the data in a list format
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    HomePage
    This class controls the backend of the Homepage Notable features here are: the linegraph, the stopwatch, and the various button to take us to others activities (profile, profile settings, statistics, analysis)
    LoginPage
    the user is going to be asked to enter their credentials in order to log into their personal account
    MainActivity
    this is the main page, the user is going to be landing on this page when they first open the application the user is going to be prompted to either the login or sign-up page
    myFirebaseMessagingService
    This class is responsible for the notifications It interacts with notifications with the Firebase Messaging service
    SignUpInfo
    activity which acts as a preamble for the sign up page
    SignUpPage
    this is a sign up page where the user is going to be entering their information and the information is going to be stored into the firebase
    StatisticsHelper
    This class is responsible for calculating the relevant statistcs for each metric based on their history arrays
    StatisticsPage
    This class controls the backend of the statistics page This class initializes every component on the page and calculates the statistics for every metric
    User
    This class represents each user and their biometrics
    UserProfile
    This class handles the backend of the profile page Fetches newest info for each user profile, displays user info
    UserProfileSettings
    This class is responsible for the backend of the user profile settings page.
